pe=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6933\">−1</script></span> and <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-6934-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32534\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32535\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32536\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6934\">1</script></span>, inclusive. A value of <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-6935-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32537\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32538\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32539\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.222em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">r</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32540\" class=\"mjx-mo MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.058em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">=</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32541\" class=\"mjx-mn MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">0</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6935\">r = 0</script></span> indicates that there is no linear association. A value of <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-6936-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32542\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32543\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32544\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.222em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">r</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32545\" class=\"mjx-mo MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.058em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">=</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32546\" class=\"mjx-mo MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.277em; padding-bottom: 0.441em;\">−</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32547\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6936\">r = -1</script></span> or <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-6937-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32548\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32549\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32550\" class=\"mjx-mi\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I\" style=\"padding-top: 0.222em; padding-bottom: 0.277em;\">r</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32551\" class=\"mjx-mo MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.058em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">=</span></span><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32552\" class=\"mjx-mn MJXc-space3\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.332em;\">1</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6937\">r = 1</script></span> indicates that there is a perfect linear association.\n\nTo interpret the correlation, one must discuss <strong>strength</strong> and <strong>direction</strong>. Since it's a measure of linear association, the form of the graph will always be linear. Therefore, since the correlation is <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-6938-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.82</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32553\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32554\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-32555\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">0.82</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0.82</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-6938\">0.82</script></span>, the correlation is <strong>strong</strong>, while also being <strong>positive</strong>. \n\n<strong>Choice 'D'</strong> is correct. ",
